[src:ramda-functional/page-p02] The step function is used as the iterator function in reduce.
[src:ramda-functional/page-p02] The result function is used to convert the final accumulator into the return type and in most cases is R.identity.
[src:ramda-functional/page-p02] The init function is used to provide the initial accumulator.
