[src:ramda-functional/page-p03] Be cautious of mutating and returning the accumulator.
[src:ramda-functional/page-p03] If you reuse it across invocations, it will continue to accumulate onto the same value.
[src:ramda-functional/page-p03] The general recommendation is to always return a new value.
[src:ramda-functional/page-p03] If you can't do so for performance reasons, then be sure to reinitialize the accumulator on each invocation.
