[src:ramda-functional/page-p04] If more arguments are passed to the returned function than transformer functions, those arguments are passed directly to `fn` as additional parameters.
[src:ramda-functional/page-p04] If you expect additional arguments that don't need to be transformed, although you can ignore them, it's best to pass an identity function so that the new function reports the correct arity.
